summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from E. B. Wallace and Carrie L. Wallace, his wife, of the City of Seattle, State of Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated January 3rd, in the year of our Lord One Thousand Nine Hundred Eleven (1911), to certain tract of land situated in Section Nine (9), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M., in the County of King, State of Washington.
